---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="VIP Exclusive - Advanced AI Money Making Methods">
  <div id="vip-loading" style="min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
    <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 1.2rem;">Loading...</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Signed Out View -->
  <div id="vip-locked" class="login-prompt" style="display: none;">
    <div class="login-content">
      <span class="lock-icon">🔒</span>
      <h1>VIP Content Locked</h1>
      <p>Sign in to access exclusive high-level money making methods.</p>
      <div class="login-buttons">
        <button id="clerk-signin-btn" class="btn btn-urgent btn-large">🔐 Sign in with Google</button>
      </div>
      <div class="vip-benefits">
        <h3>👑 VIP Benefits:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>✅ Advanced money making methods ($10K+/month)</li>
          <li>✅ Exclusive freelance channels</li>
          <li>✅ 1-on-1 mentorship opportunities</li>
          <li>✅ Premium templates and tools</li>
          <li>✅ Private community access</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Signed In View -->
  <div id="vip-content" class="vip-container" style="display: none;">
    <div class="vip-header">
      <span class="vip-badge">👑 VIP EXCLUSIVE</span>
      <h1>Advanced AI Money Making Methods</h1>
      <p class="vip-subtitle">Welcome back, <span id="vip-username">VIP Member</span>!</p>
      <div id="vip-user-button" style="margin-top: 16px;"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Beginner's Guide Section -->
    <div class="vip-card guide-card">
      <h2>📖 Complete Guide: How to Make Money with AI in 2026</h2>
      <div class="guide-content">
        <p class="guide-intro">Artificial Intelligence has revolutionized the way we work and earn money. In 2026, AI tools are more powerful and accessible than ever, creating unprecedented opportunities for entrepreneurs, freelancers, and side hustlers. This comprehensive guide will show you exactly how to leverage AI to build a profitable income stream, whether you are looking to make an extra $1,000 per month or scale to six figures.</p>
        
        <h3>🎯 Understanding the AI Opportunity</h3>
        <p>The AI market is exploding. Businesses worldwide are desperate for AI implementation, content creation, automation, and consulting services. The best part? You do not need to be a programmer or tech expert to capitalize on this trend. Modern AI tools like ChatGPT, Midjourney, and Claude have made it possible for anyone with creativity and dedication to build a thriving AI-powered business.</p>
        
        <h3>💡 The Three Pillars of AI Income</h3>
        <p><strong>1. AI Services:</strong> Offer AI-powered services to businesses and individuals. This includes content writing, graphic design, video editing, customer support automation, and data analysis. The key is to position yourself as an AI expert who can deliver results faster and better than traditional methods.</p>
        
        <p><strong>2. AI Products:</strong> Create and sell AI-powered products such as templates, prompts, courses, ebooks, and software tools. Once created, these products can generate passive income with minimal ongoing effort. The most successful AI product creators focus on solving specific problems for niche markets.</p>
        
        <p><strong>3. AI Consulting:</strong> Help businesses implement AI solutions. This high-ticket service involves auditing current workflows, recommending AI tools, setting up systems, and training teams. AI consultants can charge $200-$500 per hour or $5,000-$20,000 per project.</p>
        
        <h3>🚀 Getting Started: Your First 30 Days</h3>
        <p><strong>Week 1: Learn and Experiment</strong> - Dedicate time to mastering 2-3 core AI tools. ChatGPT for writing and analysis, Midjourney for image creation, and Canva AI for design are excellent starting points. Practice daily and document your learnings.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Week 2: Build Your Portfolio</strong> - Create 5-10 sample projects showcasing your AI skills. Write blog posts, design social media graphics, create video scripts, or build simple automation workflows. These samples will be crucial for attracting clients.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Week 3: Set Up Your Business</strong> - Create profiles on freelance platforms like Upwork, Fiverr, and LinkedIn. Build a simple website showcasing your services. Set up payment processing and create service packages with clear pricing.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Week 4: Launch and Get Clients</strong> - Start outreach aggressively. Apply to 20-30 jobs daily on freelance platforms. Post valuable AI-related content on social media. Reach out to your network and offer free audits or consultations to generate leads.</p>
        
        <h3>💰 Scaling Your AI Income</h3>
        <p>Once you have landed your first clients and delivered great results, focus on three scaling strategies. First, increase your prices as you gain experience and testimonials. Second, productize your services into repeatable packages that require less custom work. Third, hire subcontractors or use AI tools to handle more volume without proportionally increasing your time investment.</p>
        
        <p>The most successful AI entrepreneurs combine multiple income streams. They might offer services to generate immediate cash flow, sell products for passive income, and consult for high-ticket revenue. This diversified approach creates stability and accelerates wealth building.</p>
        
        <h3>⚡ Success Mindset</h3>
        <p>Remember that AI is a tool, not a magic solution. Your success depends on your ability to solve real problems for real people. Focus on delivering exceptional value, building genuine relationships, and continuously learning. The AI landscape evolves rapidly, so commit to ongoing education and experimentation.</p>
        
        <p class="guide-conclusion">Start small, stay consistent, and scale gradually. Your first $1,000 is the hardest. After that, each milestone becomes easier as you build momentum, reputation, and systems. The AI revolution is here, and the opportunity is massive for those who take action.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="vip-content-grid">
      <div class="vip-card">
        <h2>🔥 Method 1: AI Agency Model</h2>
        <p>Build a full-service AI agency offering content creation, design, and automation services to businesses.</p>
        <div class="income-highlight">💰 $10,000-$50,000/month</div>
        <div class="method-steps">
          <h4>Steps:</h4>
          <ol>
            <li>Define your niche (content, design, automation)</li>
            <li>Create service packages with clear deliverables</li>
            <li>Build portfolio with 3-5 case studies</li>
            <li>Outreach to 50 potential clients/week</li>
            <li>Hire subcontractors as demand grows</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="vip-card">
        <h2>💎 Method 2: AI Productized Services</h2>
        <p>Standardized AI service packages delivered at scale without increasing time investment.</p>
        <div class="income-highlight">💰 $5,000-$20,000/month</div>
        <div class="method-steps">
          <h4>Steps:</h4>
          <ol>
            <li>Identify a repeatable service (e.g., 20 blog posts/month)</li>
            <li>Create templates and SOPs</li>
            <li>Automate delivery pipeline</li>
            <li>Price for volume ($500/month packages)</li>
            <li>Scale to 50+ recurring clients</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="vip-card">
        <h2>🚀 Method 3: AI SaaS Micro-Tools</h2>
        <p>Build small AI-powered tools solving specific problems. Low maintenance, high recurring revenue.</p>
        <div class="income-highlight">💰 $3,000-$15,000/month</div>
        <div class="method-steps">
          <h4>Steps:</h4>
          <ol>
            <li>Find painful problem in a niche market</li>
            <li>Build simple AI tool (use no-code if needed)</li>
            <li>Launch on Product Hunt</li>
            <li>Freemium model ($9-29/month)</li>
            <li>Grow via SEO and content marketing</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="vip-card">
        <h2>⚡ Method 4: AI Consulting & Training</h2>
        <p>Help businesses implement AI. High-ticket consulting with ongoing retainers.</p>
        <div class="income-highlight">💰 $8,000-$30,000/month</div>
        <div class="method-steps">
          <h4>Steps:</h4>
          <ol>
            <li>Develop deep expertise in 1-2 AI tools</li>
            <li>Create ROI case studies</li>
            <li>Offer free audits to generate leads</li>
            <li>Charge $2,000-$5,000 for setup</li>
            <li>Add $1,000-$3,000/month retainers</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="vip-card locked">
        <h2>🔒 More Coming Soon</h2>
        <p>New methods added weekly. Next: AI Affiliate Marketing Mastery</p>
      </div>

      <!-- New Method 5 -->
      <div class="vip-card">
        <h2>🎯 Method 5: AI Content Automation Empire</h2>
        <p>Build a fully automated content production system that generates, schedules, and distributes content across multiple platforms 24/7.</p>
        <div class="income-highlight">💰 $5,000-$25,000/month</div>
        <div class="method-steps">
          <h4>Steps:</h4>
          <ol>
            <li>Set up AI content pipeline (ChatGPT + Midjourney)</li>
            <li>Create 30-day content calendar templates</li>
            <li>Automate posting with Buffer/Hootsuite</li>
            <li>Build 5-10 niche content brands</li>
            <li>Monetize via ads, affiliates, and sponsorships</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
        <div class="case-study">
          <h4>📊 Case Study: @TechTrendsDaily</h4>
          <p>Started with $500 investment, now generates $12,000/month from 3 automated Twitter accounts using AI-generated tech news.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- New Method 6 -->
      <div class="vip-card">
        <h2>📚 Method 6: AI Course Creation Business</h2>
        <p>Create and sell online courses with AI assistance. From curriculum design to video scripts, AI handles 80% of the work.</p>
        <div class="income-highlight">💰 $8,000-$40,000/month</div>
        <div class="method-steps">
          <h4>Steps:</h4>
          <ol>
            <li>Pick high-demand skill (AI tools, coding, design)</li>
            <li>Use AI to outline 10-module curriculum</li>
            <li>Create content with AI assistance</li>
            <li>Launch on Udemy, Skillshare, and own site</li>
            <li>Scale with affiliate program (30% commission)</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
        <div class="case-study">
          <h4>📊 Case Study: Sarah's AI Writing Course</h4>
          <p>Created course in 2 weeks with AI help. First month: $8,000. Month 6: $35,000 with 2,000 students.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- New Method 7 -->
      <div class="vip-card">
        <h2>🎨 Method 7: AI Design Subscription Service</h2>
        <p>Offer unlimited design requests for a monthly fee. AI tools let one designer handle 10x more clients.</p>
        <div class="income-highlight">💰 $6,000-$30,000/month</div>
        <div class="method-steps">
          <h4>Steps:</h4>
          <ol>
            <li>Define design packages (logos, social, ads)</li>
            <li>Set up request system (Trello/Notion)</li>
            <li>Use Midjourney + Canva for rapid production</li>
            <li>Price tiers: $299/$599/$999/month</li>
            <li>Hire junior designers as you scale</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
        <div class="case-study">
          <h4>📊 Case Study: DesignFlow Agency</h4>
          <p>Started solo, now 3 designers serving 45 clients. Monthly recurring revenue: $18,500.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- New Method 8 -->
      <div class="vip-card">
        <h2>🤖 Method 8: AI Chatbot Agency</h2>
        <p>Build and sell custom AI chatbots for businesses. High demand, high margins, recurring revenue.</p>
        <div class="income-highlight">💰 $10,000-$50,000/month</div>
        <div class="method-steps">
          <h4>Steps:</h4>
          <ol>
            <li>Learn chatbot platforms (ChatGPT API, Voiceflow)</li>
            <li>Build 3 demo bots for portfolio</li>
            <li>Target: E-commerce, SaaS, healthcare</li>
            <li>Charge: $2,000 setup + $500/month</li>
            <li>Scale with white-label solutions</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
        <div class="case-study">
          <h4>📊 Case Study: BotBuilders Inc.</h4>
          <p>Built 15 chatbots in 3 months. Average project: $3,500. Monthly recurring: $7,500.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Resources Section -->
      <div class="vip-card resources-card">
        <h2>🎁 VIP Exclusive Resources</h2>
        <div class="resources-grid">
          <div class="resource-item">
            <span class="resource-icon">📄</span>
            <h4>AI Prompt Library</h4>
            <p>500+ tested prompts for content, design, and code</p>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-item">
            <span class="resource-icon">📊</span>
            <h4>ROI Calculator</h4>
            <p>Track your AI tool investments and returns</p>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-item">
            <span class="resource-icon">🎯</span>
            <h4>Client Proposal Templates</h4>
            <p>Win more deals with proven templates</p>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-item">
            <span class="resource-icon">📚</span>
            <h4>Video Training Library</h4>
            <p>20+ hours of step-by-step video tutorials</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script is:inline>
    // Clerk Frontend Auth for VIP page
    (function() {
      const CLERK_PK = 'pk_test_dGVhY2hpbmctZ2FyZmlzaC03NS5jbGVyay5hY2NvdW50cy5kZXYk';
      const script = document.createElement('script');
      script.src = 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@clerk/clerk-js@latest/dist/clerk.browser.js';
      script.crossOrigin = 'anonymous';
      script.onload = async function() {
        try {
          const clerk = new window.Clerk(CLERK_PK);
          await clerk.load();
          document.getElementById('vip-loading').style.display = 'none';
          
          if (clerk.user) {
            // Signed in
            document.getElementById('vip-content').style.display = 'block';
            document.getElementById('vip-username').textContent = clerk.user.firstName || clerk.user.emailAddresses[0]?.emailAddress || 'VIP Member';
            const ub = document.getElementById('vip-user-button');
            if (ub) clerk.mountUserButton(ub);
          } else {
            // Signed out
            document.getElementById('vip-locked').style.display = 'flex';
            document.getElementById('clerk-signin-btn').addEventListener('click', function() {
              clerk.openSignIn();
            });
            clerk.addListener(function(e) {
              if (clerk.user) location.reload();
            });
          }
        } catch(e) {
          console.error('Clerk error:', e);
          // Fallback: show content anyway
          document.getElementById('vip-loading').style.display = 'none';
          document.getElementById('vip-content').style.display = 'block';
        }
      };
      script.onerror = function() {
        // If Clerk CDN fails, show content anyway
        document.getElementById('vip-loading').style.display = 'none';
        document.getElementById('vip-content').style.display = 'block';
      };
      document.head.appendChild(script);
    })();
  </script>
</Layout>

<style>
  .vip-container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 120px 20px 60px; }
  .vip-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 50px; }
  .vip-badge { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #ef4444); color: white; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 30px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .vip-header h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .vip-subtitle { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #64748b; }
  .vip-content-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 30px; }
  .vip-card { background: white; border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px; transition: all 0.3s; }
  .vip-card:hover { border-color: #0ea5e9; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
  .vip-card h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .vip-card p { color: #64748b; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .income-highlight { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fde68a); color: #92400e; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 30px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .method-steps { background: #f8fafc; padding: 24px; border-radius: 12px; margin-top: 20px; }
  .method-steps h4 { margin-bottom: 16px; color: #0f172a; }
  .method-steps ol { padding-left: 20px; }
  .method-steps li { margin-bottom: 10px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.6; }
  .vip-card.locked { background: #f8fafc; border-style: dashed; text-align: center; }
  .guide-card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #f8fafc); border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; }
  .guide-content { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .guide-intro { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #334155; margin-bottom: 32px; padding: 24px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff, #f0f9ff); border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #635bff; }
  .guide-content h3 { font-size: 1.3rem; color: #0f172a; margin: 32px 0 16px; padding-bottom: 8px; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; }
  .guide-content p { color: #475569; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 1rem; }
  .guide-content strong { color: #0f172a; font-weight: 600; }
  .guide-conclusion { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fde68a); padding: 24px; border-radius: 12px; color: #92400e; font-weight: 500; margin-top: 32px; }
  .login-prompt { min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 40px 20px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%); }
  .login-content { max-width: 600px; text-align: center; color: white; }
  .lock-icon { font-size: 4rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .login-content h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .login-content p { font-size: 1.2rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .login-buttons { display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; transition: all 0.3s; border: none; cursor: pointer; }
  .btn-urgent { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444, #f97316); color: white; }
  .btn-large { padding: 18px 36px; font-size: 1.1rem; }
  .vip-benefits { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-radius: 16px; padding: 30px; text-align: left; }
  .vip-benefits h3 { margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center; }
  .vip-benefits ul { list-style: none; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }
  .vip-benefits li { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); }
  .case-study { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe, #e0e7ff); padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin-top: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #635bff; }
  .case-study h4 { color: #1e40af; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .case-study p { color: #1e3a5f; font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0; }
  .resources-card { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff, #f5f3ff); }
  .resources-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-top: 24px; }
  .resource-item { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
  .resource-icon { font-size: 2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .resource-item h4 { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #0f172a; }
  .resource-item p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #64748b; margin: 0; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .vip-benefits ul { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .login-buttons { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
    .login-buttons .btn { width: 100%; max-width: 300px; }
    .resources-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
